    <h1>5.4.4 Release Notes</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h6 id=3D"id-5.4.4ReleaseNotes-July31st2015">July 31st 2015</h6>
<p>eZ announces the availability of 5.4.4, a maintenance release available =
for all users of eZ Publish Platform 5.4.</p>
<p>This release changes the coding style used in the kernel of eZ Publish t=
o PSR-2, an official PHP standard. There are no code changes; it doesn't fi=
x any bug and doesn't change behaviour. The change was done to increase int=
eroperability with other PHP projects, and ease backports of bug fixes from=
 the development branch of eZ Platform</p>
<p>Follow the <a href=3D"/display/EZP/5.4.x+Update+Instructions">5.4.x Upda=
te Instructions</a>&nbsp;to apply this update to your platforms. If you're =
migrating from 5.4.3, a simple <code>composer update ezsystems/ezpublish-ke=
rnel</code>&nbsp;should be sufficient to update.</p>
<h3 id=3D"id-5.4.4ReleaseNotes-Micro-releases">Micro-releases</h3>
<p>Some important fixes are backported to maintenance versions on a case-by=
-case basis, as micro-releases.<br><span>Run&nbsp;</span><code>composer upd=
ate ezsystems/ezpublish-kernel</code><span>&nbsp;to install them.</span></p=
>
<ul>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(51,51,51);">5.4.4.1 (Sep 9th 2015):&nbsp;</sp=
an><span style=3D"line-height: 1.42857;">fixes an issue with capitalized in=
ternationalized uris resolution (<a href=3D"https://jira.ez.no/browse/EZP-2=
4737" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">EZP-24737</a>).</span><span =
style=3D"line-height: 1.42857;">&nbsp;</span></li>
<li><span style=3D"line-height: 1.42857;">5.4.4.2 (<span>Sep 21st 2015</spa=
n>): fixes a backward incompatible change to the legacy aware routes (<a hr=
ef=3D"https://jira.ez.no/browse/EZP-24726" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"n=
ofollow">EZP-24726</a>).</span></li>
<li><span>5.4.4.3 (Sep 22st 2015): Cache clearing with Varnish is not worki=
ng on many ajax/cronjob based content updates, like&nbsp;update&nbsp;priori=
ty in admin (<a href=3D"https://jira.ez.no/browse/EZP-24755" class=3D"exter=
nal-link" rel=3D"nofollow">EZP-24755</a>).</span><span style=3D"line-height=
: 1.42857;"><br></span></li>
</ul>
